                <p class="email">bhavanidande@usf.edu</p>
                <p class="course">MS in AIBA</p>
                <p>
                    Bhavani focused on layout design and UI enhancements. She implemented the responsive navigation menu, improved styling on shared views like Login and About, and helped ensure that the portal works well across devices. Her contributions improved both usability and aesthetics.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Member 3 -->
